# Sugi Parfume Deployment Checklist

## Pre-Deployment
- [ ] All environment variables are set in Vercel
- [ ] Database connection is working
- [ ] Redis cache is accessible
- [ ] Stripe keys are configured
- [ ] Email service is set up
- [ ] All dependencies are up to date
- [ ] Tests are passing
- [ ] Build process completes successfully

## Environment Variables Required
- [ ] MONGODB_URI
- [ ] STRIPE_SECRET_KEY
- [ ] STRIPE_WEBHOOK_SECRET
- [ ] SMTP_HOST, SMTP_PORT, SMTP_USER, SMTP_PASS
- [ ] SUPPORT_EMAIL
- [ ] FRONTEND_URL
- [ ] REACT_APP_API_URL
- [ ] REACT_APP_WS_URL
- [ ] JWT_SECRET
- [ ] REDIS_URL
- [ ] PORT

## Post-Deployment
- [ ] Health endpoint responds correctly
- [ ] User registration works
- [ ] Login functionality works
- [ ] AI recommendations are functional
- [ ] Custom fragrance builder works
- [ ] Subscription system is operational
- [ ] Admin dashboard is accessible
- [ ] Email notifications are sent
- [ ] Payment processing works
- [ ] Real-time features are working

## Monitoring Setup
- [ ] Error tracking is enabled
- [ ] Performance monitoring is active
- [ ] Uptime monitoring is configured
- [ ] Log aggregation is working
- [ ] Alerts are set up for critical issues
